From: "Gene Cornelius"

> How does one pour oil into the stock oil tower without
either going really
> slow, or spilling it all over the frickin' place?
>

I make a little "funnel" out of card from some packaging. A
piece about 10x5cm bent into a U and inserted in the filler
gives a good pouring area. Then I just throw it away after.
Works for me!

